data.description: Located near the heart of downtown Dallas, this single-family home boasts a classic 1960s charm that is hard to find in today's modern world. Built in 1966, this home is a perfect blend of old-world charm and modern convenience. With a two-car garage and a spacious floor plan, there is plenty of room for residents to spread out and make the home their own.The backyard is a tranquil oasis in the heart of the city, with plenty of room for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. The mature trees provide shade and privacy, making it easy to forget that you are just minutes away from the hustle and bustle of downtown Dallas. The two-car garage is convenient for residents who need to park their cars securely and protect them from the elements.
